---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="High School Graduation Party Planning Guide" description="Plan the perfect high school graduation party with our complete guide. Themes, decorations, food ideas, photo booth setups, and custom sports centerpieces for the graduate's celebration.">
  <div class="breadcrumbs">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/">Home</a> <span>/</span> <strong>Graduation Party Guide</strong>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>The Complete Graduation Party Planning Guide</h1>
      <p>Graduation parties mark the end of a chapter and the start of a new one. For student-athletes, it's a celebration of both academic and athletic achievement.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-wrapper">
        <h2>Planning Timeline: 8 Weeks Out</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Choose date and venue</strong> — Home, hall, or restaurant</li>
          <li><strong>Set guest list estimate</strong> — Typically 30-100 guests</li>
          <li><strong>Determine budget</strong> — Average grad party costs $500-$2,000</li>
          <li><strong>Choose theme or style</strong> — Sports-themed? Classic? Casual?</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>6 Weeks Out</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Send invitations (digital or paper)</li>
          <li>Order decorations and party supplies</li>
          <li>Plan menu and arrange catering</li>
          <li>Order custom centerpieces (allow 2-3 weeks for custom 3D printed items)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Popular Graduation Party Themes for Athletes</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Sports Legacy Theme</strong> — Highlight the graduate's athletic career with displays and included sports decor</li>
          <li><strong>Team Color Bash</strong> — Decorations in school colors throughout</li>
          <li><strong>"Future [Sport] Star"</strong> — For athletes heading to college sports</li>
          <li><strong>Jersey Number Party</strong> — Everything themed around their jersey number</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Graduation Table Decor</h2>
        <p>The dessert table or gift table is a natural focal point. Graduation centerpieces that reflect your graduate's athletic career add a personal touch that standard graduation decorations can't match.</p>

        <div class="product-note">
          <p><strong>🎓 Sports-Themed Graduation Centerpieces:</strong> Custom 3D printed sports centerpieces designed in your school's colors with the graduate's jersey number or graduation year make excellent table toppers. Many graduates take them to college as a keepsake.</p>
          <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/collections/all" class="btn btn-outline" target="_blank">See Sports Graduation Centerpieces →</a>
        </div>

        <h2>Photo Booth & Memory Station Ideas</h2>
        <p>Set up a photo station with sports props (mini helmets, foam fingers, medals), a backdrop in school colors, and a "future plans" chalkboard. Include a memory table with the graduate's jerseys, trophies, and team photos from each year.</p>

        <p><a href="/decorations/" class="btn btn-outline">More Decoration Ideas →</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
